  "text": "As mentioned in the introduction, hospital episode data may be sufficient for acute hospital care requiring events. However, for chronic conditions, as illustrated here with CKD, the use [CITATION_1] of corroborating additional data when admissions are due to another event or comorbidity may be necessary.",
